WELCOME ABOARD MIDWEST EXPRESS®
We've earned our reputation as
"The best care in the airsu"
by offering passengers
luxury service for coach
fare or less.
Wide, two-across leather
seats —rated #1 for
roominess and comfort
in a nationally reported survey — add a
comfortable new "dimension" to your flight.
Gourmet meals tempt the appetite of the most
discriminating business traveler. Fine wine or
champagne is offered with our compliments.
And on some flights we even serve
fresh-baked chocolate-chip
cookies! Sit back, relax
and enjoy!
